item.title: CVE-2023-1915|2023-05-15T12:15:33.297Z -- unknown -- thumbnail%20carousel%20slider
item.description: The Thumbnail carousel slider WordPress plugin before 1.1.10 does not sanitise and escape some parameters before outputting them back in pages, leading to Reflected Cross-Site Scripting vulnerability which could be used against high privilege users such as admin.
